# Google OAuth — enables real "Continue with Google" (account picker).
# 1. https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID → Web application
# 3. Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173 (and your production URL)
# 4. Authorized redirect URIs: http://localhost:5173 (same origin; popup flow)
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Supabase Configuration
# 1. Create account at https://supabase.com
# 2. Create a new project
# 3. Copy URL and Anon Key from project settings
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

